!changeto help/fr/sheetpage.phtml

<h3>Using a document block for worksheet presentation</h3>

You may put the address of a document block
(such as <span class="tt wims_fname">c1/main</span>) to be the presentation page of the work sheet.
The document itself need not be readable by participants.
<p>Leave this field blank if you want to use the standard presentation page.</p>
<p>
Links to individual exercises should be defined using the command
    <span class="tt wims_code_variable">\exercise</span>.</p>
You can use the following pre-defined variables:
<ul>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\scorerequire</span>
   Required points of each exercise of the sheet
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\scoregot</span>
   Participant's point achievements on each exercise (i0)
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\scoremean</span>
   Liste de l'indicateur i1 pour chaque exercice de la feuille.
   Participant's average score on each exercise (i1)
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\scorebests</span>
   Liste des sommes cumulatives des N meilleurs scores pour chaque exercice de la feuille (N est le nombre de points requis divisé par 10).
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\scorelevels</span>
   Liste de l'indicateur i2 pour chaque exercice de la feuille.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\scorealltries</span>
   Liste du nombre de tentatives de chaque exercice de la feuille.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\expiration</span>
   Expiration date of the sheet (format yyyymmdd).
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\today</span>
   Date of today (format yyyymmdd).
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\user_login</span>
   l'identifiant du participant.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\user_firstname</span>
   le prénom du participant.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\user_lastname</span>
   le nom du participant.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\class_code</span>
   le numéro de la classe.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\title</span>
   le titre de la feuille.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\desc</span>
   le descriptif de la feuille.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\nbexo</span>
   le nombre d'exercices de la feuille.
 </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\sheet</span>
  le numéro de la feuille.
  </li>
 <li><span class="tt wims_code_variable">\infoexo$$k</span>
   les informations sur l'exercice k de la feuille.
 </li>
</ul>
<p>All the score parameters are lists of numbers, each member of the list
corresponding to the number for an exercise of the sheet.</p>

<b>For example</b>, if you are creating worksheet number 5,
  for example write the following instructions
<pre>
\exercise{5/1} : Score required: \scorerequire[1]
                 Score obtained: \scoregot[1]

\exercise{5/2} : Score required: \scorerequire[2]
                 Score obtained: \scoregot[2]

\exercise{5/3}{Un autre titre}: Score required \scorerequire[3]
                Score obtained: \scoregot[3]
</pre>
